This package contains XIncProc XInclude implementation

See: Description

    Class Description
    XIncProcCLI
    Custom executor for CLI
    XIncProcConfiguration
    XIncProcConfiguration class holds configuration options for XIncProcEngine.
    XIncProcEngine
    This class contains useful methods to manage a XMLFilter for xinclusions and to parse content with xinclude tags.
    XIncProcErrorListener
    This class is a listener .
    XIncProcUtils
    This class provide utilities constants, variables and methods for the XIncProcEngine.
